# Members database (Neon Postgres)

- All persistence is Postgres (`members`, `password_resets`, `merch_orders`).
- Use `db.members` or `routes.member_store`; HTTP API in `routes/api_routes.py`.
- Schema: `db/schema.sql`. Human docs: `docs/DATABASE.md`.
- Passwords: bcrypt only; strip passwords from all API JSON.
- Scripts: `scripts/db/apply_schema.py`, `scripts/db/set_admin.py`, `scripts/db/import_members_json.py`.
